T(0)=0
 T(n) = \sum_{j=0}^{\lfloor \log_2 n \rfloor} (2^j \times 1) = 2^{\lfloor \log_2 n \rfloor+1} -1.
 \log_2 n - 1 < \lfloor \log_2 n \rfloor \le \log_2 n
n < 2^{\lfloor \log_2 n \rfloor+1} \le 2n \quad \text{and} \quad n-1 < T(n) \le 2n-1.
T(n) \in \Theta(n).
